                "title": "Terms of Use"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "NVIDIA Base Command Manager 10.24.07 and earlier versions do not contain this vulnerability.<div>Use this security update to resolve the issue as follows:</div><div><ul><li>Update to the most recent version of CMdaemon on the head nodes and in all software images.</li><li>Update the nodes by rebooting them or by resynchronizing them against the software image.</li></ul></div>",
